text.section:
All offenses classified as violations under this chapter shall be prepayable except for:
Violations of KRS 235.240 and 235.285;
An offense where evidence of the commission of the offense or another offense was seized and the citation is so marked and a court date set;
The offense is cited with another offense that is not prepayable and the citation is so marked and a court date set; or
An arrest is made under KRS 431.015.
